1015
01:08:04.480 --> 01:08:08.211
How could they remember what
they're being forced to forget?

1016
01:08:29.605 --> 01:08:31.095
What the hell?

1017
01:09:32.735 --> 01:09:33.929
Holy shit.

1018
01:09:54.390 --> 01:09:55.379
Where are they?

1019
01:09:55.457 --> 01:09:56.446
I don't know.

1020
01:09:56.525 --> 01:09:58.083
- I tried to tell you...
- You don't know?

1021
01:09:58.160 --> 01:09:59.525
I want the video
played back.

1022
01:09:59.595 --> 01:10:01.529
Sir. it didn't
record.

1023
01:10:01.597 --> 01:10:02.689
It did. but nothing came out.

1024
01:10:02.765 --> 01:10:04.596
Come on! Bullshit!

1025
01:10:04.700 --> 01:10:07.134
Ryan. pull yourself
together. man.

1026
01:10:16.212 --> 01:10:18.146
- Calm down. Mom.
- What the hell happened?

1027
01:10:18.214 --> 01:10:20.375
They took my baby.
They took her.

1028
01:10:20.449 --> 01:10:21.746
Who?

1029
01:10:21.817 --> 01:10:23.216
- They took my baby.
- What is she talking about?

1030
01:10:23.285 --> 01:10:24.513
Someone kidnapped
Ashley.

1031
01:10:24.587 --> 01:10:26.316
Okay. I want this entire house searched.

1032
01:10:26.388 --> 01:10:27.912
I want everybody
inside. outside.

1033
01:10:27.990 --> 01:10:30.015
...going through these
premises top to bottom.

1034
01:10:30.092 --> 01:10:31.218
Ronnie. what'd you see?

1035
01:10:31.293 --> 01:10:33.056
Nothing. I came in
here and she was gone.

1036
01:10:33.128 --> 01:10:34.857
- What's going on here?
- August. listen to me.

1037
01:10:34.930 --> 01:10:35.988
I'm listening.

1038
01:10:36.065 --> 01:10:37.726
A beam of light
came down...

1039
01:10:37.900 --> 01:10:40.198
...and they took her
into the sky.

1040
01:10:40.269 --> 01:10:43.636
They took my little girl
up into the sky. I saw it!

1041
01:10:43.706 --> 01:10:44.695
Through the
ceiling?

1042
01:10:44.773 --> 01:10:45.831
August. I saw it!

1043
01:10:45.908 --> 01:10:46.932
Through the ceiling?

1044
01:10:47.009 --> 01:10:48.772
Yes. They took her
through the ceiling.

1045
01:10:48.844 --> 01:10:49.970
What is this craziness?

1046
01:10:50.045 --> 01:10:51.069
What the hell
is going on here?

1047
01:10:51.146 --> 01:10:52.272
I couldn't stop it.

1048
01:10:52.348 --> 01:10:53.713
Okay. Everybody
clear this room!

1049
01:10:53.782 --> 01:10:54.806
I want everybody
out of here.

1050
01:10:54.883 --> 01:10:57.147
...except Ronnie
and Abbey!

1051
01:10:57.253 --> 01:10:58.982
Ronnie. sit down right
there. please. Okay?

1052
01:10:59.054 --> 01:11:00.851
- Abbey. you sit down.
- Please sit down. My baby.

1053
01:11:00.923 --> 01:11:03.289
Okay? Sit here. I want
to talk to you. okay?

1054
01:11:03.359 --> 01:11:04.417
You just tell me.

1055
01:11:04.493 --> 01:11:06.188
Listen. less than five
hours after I arrest you...

1056
01:11:06.262 --> 01:11:07.991
...your daughter
goes missing.

1057
01:11:08.063 --> 01:11:09.052
I told you.

1058
01:11:09.131 --> 01:11:10.120
Yeah. but
that's horseshit.

1059
01:11:10.199 --> 01:11:11.393
We know that
that's not real.

1060
01:11:11.467 --> 01:11:12.525
Tell me
what happened.

1061
01:11:12.601 --> 01:11:13.863
You had an officer
outside my house.

1062
01:11:13.936 --> 01:11:14.960
Yes. we had
an officer outside.

1063
01:11:15.037 --> 01:11:16.368
- What did he see?
- He didn't see anything.

1064
01:11:16.438 --> 01:11:18.338
He says that the videotape
wasn't playing. Now. just tell me.

1065
01:11:18.407 --> 01:11:19.431
Where is she?
Listen. Abbey!

1066
01:11:19.508 --> 01:11:20.497
What did he see?

1067
01:11:20.576 --> 01:11:22.043
- Get him in here right now!
- You listen to me now.

1068
01:11:22.111 --> 01:11:23.476
- You know what's real!
- I want to know what he saw.

1069
01:11:23.545 --> 01:11:25.342
- You know what's real!
- You had an officer outside my house!

1070
01:11:25.414 --> 01:11:26.438
God damn it!
Where is she?

1071
01:11:26.515 --> 01:11:28.142
You
were supposed to protect us!

1072
01:11:28.217 --> 01:11:32.017
Abbey. where is she. God damn
it? You tell me where she is!

1073
01:11:32.888 --> 01:11:35.220
Where is Ashley?
Where is she?

1074
01:11:35.291 --> 01:11:37.191
Mom!
Can't you stop?

1075
01:11:37.559 --> 01:11:38.548
It's okay.
It's okay.

1076
01:11:38.627 --> 01:11:40.117
Please. just stop!

1077
01:11:40.195 --> 01:11:44.097
Abbey. you haven't been
right in the head since Will.

1078
01:11:44.800 --> 01:11:46.199
You just haven't been right in the head.

1079
01:11:46.268 --> 01:11:47.792
You haven't
found his killer.

1080
01:11:47.870 --> 01:11:49.064
What?

1081
01:11:49.538 --> 01:11:51.028
You still haven't
found his killer.

1082
01:11:51.106 --> 01:11:53.301
No. Abbey. we have. Yes. we have.

1083
01:11:53.375 --> 01:11:55.536
He's still out there.
He's still out there.

1084
01:11:55.611 --> 01:11:58.671
No. Listen. I'm removing
him from your custody.

1085
01:11:58.781 --> 01:11:59.975
- No.
- Yes. I am...

1086
01:12:00.049 --> 01:12:02.347
...and find a lawyer.
because you've run out.

1087
01:12:02.418 --> 01:12:03.407
...of all the goodwill
I've got. okay?

1088
01:12:03.485 --> 01:12:04.645
He's not
gonna take you away.

1089
01:12:04.720 --> 01:12:07.154
Guys. get in here. We're removing
Ronnie from Abbey's custody!

1090
01:12:07.222 --> 01:12:08.883
No. No. you're
not! You will not...

1091
01:12:08.957 --> 01:12:10.788
- Let go!
- You will not.

1092
01:12:10.859 --> 01:12:12.417
- No. No.
- Let go!

1093
01:12:12.494 --> 01:12:13.984
No. No. no.
Baby. baby. no!

1094
01:12:14.063 --> 01:12:15.087
Let go. Let go.

1095
01:12:15.164 --> 01:12:17.598
No. no. You're not taking my boy!

1096
01:12:17.666 --> 01:12:19.065
- I'm sorry.
- You're not taking my boy!

1097
01:12:19.134 --> 01:12:20.931
He'll be safe! He'll be safe!

1098
01:12:21.003 --> 01:12:22.868
You're not
taking my boy!

1099
01:12:43.325 --> 01:12:44.417
God!

1100
01:12:48.530 --> 01:12:49.895
My babies!

1101
01:12:56.205 --> 01:12:58.105
Why are you doing this?

1102
01:13:00.442 --> 01:13:04.276
All I realized. that they
weren't going to be able to find her.

1103
01:13:04.713 --> 01:13:06.647
That I would have
to do it on my own.

1104
01:13:06.715 --> 01:13:08.615
But you couldn't leave.

1105
01:13:09.618 --> 01:13:14.146
No. that's not what I mean. I had to...

1106
01:13:17.226 --> 01:13:20.821
To find a way
to go directly to them...

1107
01:13:21.697 --> 01:13:24.097
...directly to
the source.

1108
01:14:41.043 --> 01:14:43.136
I know what I saw. but I...

1109
01:14:46.615 --> 01:14:48.708
I can't accept it.
I can't.

1110
01:14:52.120 --> 01:14:55.021
So please don't ask
me to. because I can't.

1111
01:14:57.659 --> 01:15:00.093
I still have to
do this.

1112
01:15:00.162 --> 01:15:01.652
But Scott. you...

1113
01:15:09.271 --> 01:15:10.636
Is this the right way?

1114
01:15:10.706 --> 01:15:11.900
I don't know.

1115
01:15:13.609 --> 01:15:15.474
I don't have a choice.

1116
01:15:19.348 --> 01:15:22.374
Yeah.
I know you don't.

1117
01:15:29.658 --> 01:15:31.888
Your eyes are
feeling heavier.

1118
01:15:33.829 --> 01:15:36.389
Seven. six...

1119
01:15:38.600 --> 01:15:41.763
...five. four...

1120
01:15:43.805 --> 01:15:46.740
...three. two.

1121
01:15:47.876 --> 01:15:50.367
...and one.

1122
01:15:51.446 --> 01:15:52.845
- Abbey?
- Yes.

1123
01:15:53.615 --> 01:15:58.052
Let's go back three days. to Tuesday...

1124
01:15:59.521 --> 01:16:02.581
when you were giving
dictation in your bedroom.

1125
01:16:03.091 --> 01:16:04.456
- Yes.
- Good.

1126
01:16:05.060 --> 01:16:08.427
Now. what happened after
you finished your dictation?

1127
01:16:10.265 --> 01:16:15.635
...remains unexplained.
and worse. unsolved...

1128
01:16:17.139 --> 01:16:18.470
...like Will.

1129
01:16:21.276 --> 01:16:22.300
Are you
sleeping?

1130
01:16:22.377 --> 01:16:23.401
Yes.

1131
01:16:25.747 --> 01:16:27.476
What happened
next?

1132
01:16:32.321 --> 01:16:33.310
There's an owl.

1133
01:16:33.388 --> 01:16:34.650
The owl.

1134
01:16:35.791 --> 01:16:37.691
- It's looking down at me.
- It's looking down at me.

1135
01:16:37.759 --> 01:16:40.353
Is it the same owl
your patients see?

1136
01:16:41.163 --> 01:16:42.494
- Yes.
- Yes.

1137
01:16:43.298 --> 01:16:45.732
- It's smiling.
- It's smiling.

1138
01:16:47.903 --> 01:16:49.200
I don't like it
when it smiles.

1139
01:16:49.271 --> 01:16:50.966
I don't like it
when it smiles.

1140
01:16:51.039 --> 01:16:53.473
What do you mean.
smiling?

1141
01:16:53.609 --> 01:16:54.633
I don't know
what I mean.

1142
01:16:54.710 --> 01:16:55.802
I don't know
what I mean.

1143
01:16:55.877 --> 01:16:58.277
- I don't want to know.
- I don't want to know.

1144
01:16:58.347 --> 01:17:01.783
Well. it's too late to
forget what you already know.

1145
01:17:01.850 --> 01:17:03.215
Tell me what you see.

1146
01:17:07.222 --> 01:17:09.156
- It's not an owl.
- It's not an owl.

1147
01:17:44.326 --> 01:17:46.988
God. help me! Help me!

1148
01:17:50.098 --> 01:17:51.326
No.

1149
01:17:51.400 --> 01:17:53.027
No! No!

1150
01:17:53.335 --> 01:17:55.530
Help me! Help me!

1151
01:18:00.308 --> 01:18:02.469
Help me! Help!

1152
01:18:03.845 --> 01:18:06.109
Abbey.
what is it?

1153
01:18:06.715 --> 01:18:08.182
God. help me.

1154
01:18:08.850 --> 01:18:13.412
There are too many of
them. It burns. It hurts!

1155
01:18:19.661 --> 01:18:23.495
No. no! Please!
Stop it. No.

1156
01:18:30.906 --> 01:18:33.204
It's sticking
into my shoulder.

1157
01:20:53.815 --> 01:20:56.045
So what
happened in that room?

1158
01:20:56.818 --> 01:20:58.149
They came...

1159
01:20:59.588 --> 01:21:02.455
...and we were...

1160
01:21:05.627 --> 01:21:06.958
We were...

1161
01:21:09.798 --> 01:21:11.425
They abducted us.

1162
01:21:12.200 --> 01:21:16.193
All of us. but brought
us back that same night.

1163
01:21:19.140 --> 01:21:21.665
We don't remember
where they took us.

1164
01:21:23.678 --> 01:21:25.578
...or what
they did to us.

1165
01:21:26.114 --> 01:21:31.347
Even with hypnosis.
it's black.

1166
01:21:35.857 --> 01:21:37.722
Your voice.
or its voice...

1167
01:21:38.860 --> 01:21:40.452
...said it was God.

1168
01:21:42.197 --> 01:21:44.131
What do
you believe?

1169
01:21:44.199 --> 01:21:45.598
I believe...

1170
01:21:46.067 --> 01:21:49.366
It's hard.
but I believe.

1171
01:21:49.938 --> 01:21:52.532
...the things I've seen...

1172
01:21:53.408 --> 01:21:56.036
...the presence I've felt.

1173
01:21:56.978 --> 01:21:58.377
...inside of me.

1174
01:21:59.347 --> 01:22:03.841
...is beyond anything
you can imagine.

1175
01:22:04.986 --> 01:22:06.248
It was.

1176
01:22:09.457 --> 01:22:10.947
...hopelessness...

1177
01:22:11.726 --> 01:22:15.162
...so it cannot be God...

1178
01:22:16.131 --> 01:22:17.598
...but it can...

1179
01:22:19.000 --> 01:22:20.831
It can pretend to be.

1180
01:22:22.971 --> 01:22:24.996
And what about Ashley?

1181
01:22:25.073 --> 01:22:26.540
What about...

1182
01:22:26.608 --> 01:22:27.700
And what about
your daughter?

1183
01:22:29.344 --> 01:22:30.504
She...

1184
01:22:32.480 --> 01:22:34.880
I had to recover
from that night.

1185
01:22:36.384 --> 01:22:39.080
It took me a couple
of days to wake up.

1186
01:23:20.762 --> 01:23:22.627
Abel...

1187
01:23:22.697 --> 01:23:24.028
It's...

1188
01:23:25.333 --> 01:23:27.130
It's okay.
It's okay.

1189
01:23:27.202 --> 01:23:28.191
What is this?

1190
01:23:28.269 --> 01:23:29.930
Look. I have
to apologize.

1191
01:23:30.772 --> 01:23:31.761
I...

1192
01:23:33.575 --> 01:23:36.476
I'm sorry. I really
hate to have to do this.

1193
01:23:37.278 --> 01:23:40.270
when you're in this
condition that you're in.

1194
01:23:44.652 --> 01:23:45.641
It's okay.

1195
01:23:45.720 --> 01:23:46.744
So...

1196
01:23:47.222 --> 01:23:50.055
well. I still have that
question for you. Abbey.

1197
01:23:57.198 --> 01:23:58.825
How did Will die?

1198
01:24:04.339 --> 01:24:06.068
He was murdered.

1199
01:24:06.141 --> 01:24:08.109
No. Abbey.

1200
01:24:11.513 --> 01:24:15.244
Abbey. he's going to show you
something that will upset you...

1201
01:24:16.051 --> 01:24:19.680
...but it has to be done.

1202
01:24:20.855 --> 01:24:22.220
Understand?

1203
01:24:29.898 --> 01:24:31.889
This is the head
of a man.

1204
01:24:36.071 --> 01:24:37.732
who used this gun.

1205
01:24:42.277 --> 01:24:43.369
Okay?

1206
01:24:47.916 --> 01:24:52.216
Yeah. It was suicide.
Abbey. It was suicide.

1207
01:24:52.787 --> 01:24:56.120
He took a pistol. shot
himself in the head.

1208
01:24:56.357 --> 01:24:58.222
There was no intruder.

1209
01:24:58.860 --> 01:25:03.092
There was no knife. Just him with
his pistol at the side of your bed.

1210
01:25:04.532 --> 01:25:07.933
He's not that man. He wouldn't
do that. He wouldn't do that.

1211
01:25:08.002 --> 01:25:11.802
He wouldn't do that to us. He
wouldn't do that to his family.

1212
01:25:16.277 --> 01:25:18.507
Tell him he's wrong. Tell him.

1213
01:25:19.547 --> 01:25:24.780
I'm a psychologist. and I
would have known... Christ.

1214
01:25:26.321 --> 01:25:28.915
I would have known
if he was gonna...

1215
01:25:29.257 --> 01:25:31.418
Abbey. Abbey.

1216
01:25:31.493 --> 01:25:32.755
You can't blame yourself.

1217
01:25:32.827 --> 01:25:35.660
...for something that was
going on in his head.

1218
01:25:37.132 --> 01:25:41.865
Who knows what he'd learned.
what he didn't share...

1219
01:25:43.505 --> 01:25:45.268
...and finally
what broke him?

1220
01:25:45.340 --> 01:25:47.399
Now you know the reality.

1221
01:25:49.310 --> 01:25:53.076
I'm gonna ask you for
the last time. Tell me.

1222
01:25:56.718 --> 01:25:58.686
What happened
to Ashley?

1223
01:25:59.154 --> 01:26:01.918
Tell me. Abbey.

1224
01:26:05.894 --> 01:26:10.126
You know what happened.
You experienced it.

1225
01:26:11.866 --> 01:26:15.563
But we came back and she didn't. Abel.

1226
01:26:18.072 --> 01:26:22.202
Tell him. Tell him what happened.

1227
01:26:33.588 --> 01:26:35.852
Something took my daughter.

1228
01:26:37.825 --> 01:26:42.125
I don't know what. I
don't... I don't know how.

1229
01:26:46.601 --> 01:26:49.968
I don't know what it was.
but you have to believe me.

1230
01:26:52.006 --> 01:26:54.304
You have to
believe me. please.

1231
01:26:56.044 --> 01:26:57.238
Please.

1232
01:26:59.280 --> 01:27:00.406
Please.

1233
01:27:00.481 --> 01:27:02.039
It's difficult
to go back.

1234
01:27:04.319 --> 01:27:05.547
Go back?

1235
01:27:07.088 --> 01:27:11.047
Back over the line
from fiction to reality.

1236
01:27:15.863 --> 01:27:19.060
You can't just stop being
insane whenever you want to.

1237
01:27:22.136 --> 01:27:25.628
It's the kind of thing
that stays with you forever.

1238
01:27:29.877 --> 01:27:31.902
So Will committed suicide?

1239
01:27:34.682 --> 01:27:35.740
Yes.

1240
01:27:37.585 --> 01:27:40.554
Your credibility. How do
you expect me or the audience.

1241
01:27:40.622 --> 01:27:42.146
...to believe anything you're saying...

1242
01:27:42.223 --> 01:27:44.157
...if you actually
hallucinated.

1243
01:27:44.225 --> 01:27:45.749
...the murder
of your husband?

1244
01:27:47.061 --> 01:27:49.188
They weren't
hallucinations.

1245
01:27:51.065 --> 01:27:52.726
I just couldn't...

1246
01:27:54.435 --> 01:27:57.063
It can be difficult
to face the truth...

1247
01:27:58.539 --> 01:28:00.029
...and with Will...

1248
01:28:01.542 --> 01:28:03.772
...that's how
I dealt with it.

1249
01:28:03.845 --> 01:28:05.642
And no matter
what you believe...

1250
01:28:06.781 --> 01:28:10.239
...the recordings
do not lie.

1251
01:28:10.852 --> 01:28:16.449
We were talking about
things that aren't normal.

1252
01:28:18.026 --> 01:28:22.759
...is dead.
... Back is broken.

1253
01:28:23.765 --> 01:28:27.166
And Ashley.
she's still gone.

1254
01:28:29.003 --> 01:28:31.972
These are hard facts.

1255
01:28:32.340 --> 01:28:34.137
They do
appear to be.

1256
01:28:34.442 --> 01:28:37.240
No. God damn it.
they are!

1257
01:28:38.379 --> 01:28:41.871
You can sit here
and speculate...

1258
01:28:42.550 --> 01:28:46.111
...but I have to
keep hope alive.

1259
01:28:48.089 --> 01:28:51.820
I have to believe
in what we're doing...

1260
01:28:52.860 --> 01:28:54.953
...my story...

1261
01:28:57.098 --> 01:28:58.759
...that it will help.

1262
01:29:00.268 --> 01:29:01.895
I have to believe.

1263
01:29:02.704 --> 01:29:07.073
...that she's still
alive somewhere...

1264
01:29:08.409 --> 01:29:09.876
...that she's safe.

1265
01:29:11.279 --> 01:29:15.181
I have to believe
that there's a chance.

1266
01:29:16.584 --> 01:29:18.779
...that I'm gonna
see her again...

1267
01:29:20.888 --> 01:29:22.753
...hold her again...

